|GKO================================================================
                      |GKBUmbral Klaive
|GKO================================================================

|YKOThe Umbral Klaive is a Guardian's most powerful weapon. Forged
through manifesting a Guardian's eurus, via the Umbra, and binding
a bane into the blade.

By default, an Umbral Klaive will be bound by an Earth bane. This
will cause the Klaive to be (chaotic), like Spirit Claws. If you
want to bind a different bane, here are the following banes to 
choose from and their syntax:

 |YKBklaive|YKO:             |WKOAn Earth Elemental is bound to the
                     klaive, causing vines to lash out
                     from it.
 
 |YKBklaive huge|YKO:        |WKOAn Earth Elemental is bound to the
                     klaive, causing vines to lash out
                     from it. This is a Grand Klaive.

 |YKBklaive living|YKO:      |WKOA Wyld Spirit is bound to the
                     klaive, causing the klaive to appear
                     to be living.

 |YKBklaive flaming|YKO:     |WKOA Fire Elemental is bound to the
                     klaive, causing the klaive to have
                     flames consuming it.

 |YKBklaive frozen|YKO:      |WKOAn Ice Elemental is bound to the
                     klaive, causing ice crystals to form
                     along the length of the blade.

 |YKBklaive humming|YKO:     |WKOAn Umbral Bane is bound to the
                     klaive, cause it to vibrate endlessly.

 |YKBklaive shocking|YKO:    |WKOA Lightning Elemental is bound to
                     the klaive, causing the blade to course
                     with electricity.

 |YKBklaive wildrage|YKO:    |WKOA Rage Spirit is bound to the
                     klaive, causing the blade itself to
                     sear it's enemies flesh.

 |YKBklaive poisoned|YKO:    |WKOA Toxin Bane is bound to the
                     klaive, causing the blade to be
                     coated in various posions.


|WKOUsable in form: |GKOMan & Crinos        |WKOCost:  |CKO150 sp
|WKORestricted to: |GKBGuardian             |WKOTimer: |CKOMedium
|RKOSyntax: |YKBklaive <type>               |WKOType:  |CKOSupport